sh notification trigger in ImGateway** - The PRD says "离线用户通过极光推送/Fire
base 触发新消息提醒". The `ImGateway.handleSendMessage` increments unread count 
in Redis but never calls `PushService.sendPush()` when the receiver is offline. 
